<br>
I'm kinda flat broke right now, so i am pretty tempted to take the offered plat.  I usually still turn it down tho.  I did accept some crap item and a velious quest gem worth about 200p for a res the other day just because it was SUPER inconvenient to me.<br>
<br>
I do love the people who get pissed when you dont take it tho :)  Turned down 100p on Sunday from a druid/necro i had to res and he sent like 3-4 tells asking me to come back and take it and he wont take no for an answer and wishes i took it.  Pretty funny really :)<br>
